benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/bundles/{bundleId}/pause - Pause a bundle

covered: PUT Method - Valid Request scenarios (TC01, TC02, TC03, TC04, TC05)
Error conditions and invalid inputs (TC06, TC08, TC09, TC13, TC14, TC15, TC16, TC17, TC18, TC19)
gaps: Rate Limiting / Throttling tests are not present
Caching behavior / caching headers (ETag, Cache-Control) are not tested
Explicit testing for 403/invalid-ownership in authorization (beyond 401) could be expanded
Explicit empty data/zero-bundles edge case (covered by TC20 as empty DB but no dedicated empty-list response path)
recommendations: Add rate limiting tests to ensure the API handles bursts or high concurrency gracefully
Add caching behavior tests (ETag/Cache-Control) to verify proper caching semantics
Add a dedicated 403 forbidden scenario for unauthorized access with valid token but insufficient permissions
Consider a dedicated test for empty dataset response shape if API can return empty payloads (beyond 404)
